15 WHEREAS, physician anesthesiologists are recognized leaders who are committed to safe
16 and high-quality patient care, educating patients on anesthesia safety and reducing the risks
17 of complications.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
19 the members of this body recognize January 26 to February 1, 2025, as Physician
20 Anesthesiologists Week at the state capitol.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
22 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
23 Georgia Society of Anesthesiologists, the public, and the press.
